Heat oven to 375 degrees F. Mix all ingredients except crabmeat and almonds in medium bowl until well blended. Stir crabmeat. Spread crabmeat mixture in ungreased pie plate, 9 x 1 1/4 inches, or shallow 1-quart casserole. Sprinkle with almonds. Bake 15 to 20 minutes or until hot and bubbly. Serve while warm to spread on crackers.